       ROT-MENS2.
                ADD 1 TO W-CONT
                IF W-CONT < 3000
                   GO TO ROT-MENS2
                ELSE
                   MOVE SPACES TO MENS
                   DISPLAY (22, 13) MENS.
       ROT-MENS-FIM.
                EXIT.
